reviewText: Combo for less than the price of each individually is why I bought this.  I'm not going to review the movies, you've probably already seen them.
Case was busted up, but all the discs are in good shape!
All movies work, brings my back a few years
Love my football movies and these are three great ones. Picture quality was great on these blu-rays.

I had to send this product back twice because it was damaged. The first time was the case and the disc holders so the disc were scratched and the 2nd time was the disc holders again so the discs were scratched. I REALLY wanted this product because I need all three movies for my sports movies collection. I was extremely disappointed!
Didn't know it was blue ray and it cost just as much to ship it back as I paid so I'm stuck with it. Can't even watch it. What a shame
The we are Marshall disc is sketched and the back of the movie case is damaged but the other two movies are fine.
Shipped quickly and was exactly as described.

The videos were OK but the box they came in was damaged I have three DVDs in a broken box I was not happy about that  because I'm sure one or all of them may wind up getting scratched and be no good to me after a couple of uses . I would appreciate a new box that holds three DVDs instead of what I have now .
Great deal on movies that I've enjoyed immensely.  No problem with quality or delivery times.
